# Environment secrets

Follow `docs/01-setup/env-and-secrets.md`.

## Required variables (backend)

```
SUPABASE_URL=
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=
PORT=3000
```

## Frontend-only (Phase 2 — not used by Express today)

```
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
VITE_API_URL=
```

## Rules

- Never commit `.env`, `.env.local`, or `.env.*.local`
- Use `.env.example` as the committed template — placeholder values only
- Do not add `SUPABSE_*` typos — correct prefix is `SUPABASE_`
- Railway: set vars in dashboard, not in repo
- CI uses placeholder Supabase vars — real secrets stay out of GitHub Actions

## Phase 2

```
# CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173
```

Set to Vercel production URL when frontend deploys.
